Holistic environmental protection

Our Eco Efficiency @ Siemens program Our Eco Efficiency @ Siemens program addresses environ-

mental factors specific to our products, systems, solutions, and services and our production. It also defines objectives for improving our environmental management: for example, by encouraging a circular economy and generally demateri- alizing our business processes.

DEGREE, Eco Efficiency @ Siemens, and our environmental initiatives give Siemens a broad range of instruments to guide our objectives in environmental protection